  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0cc752b210a5b8b4892cff0fe6244710, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  introPanel: {fileID: 818151686}
  introText: {fileID: 552072961}
  gameSceneName: GameScene
  typeSpeed: 0.05
  fullStoryText: 'We were researchers, explorers to expand humanity''s horizons.

    We
    stopped on one planet for what we thought was a routine survey. When we left,
    something came back with us.

    And now I awaken from cryosleep to what remains.

    One
    thing is for certain: the ship is not what it used to be.

    T-0:30 until self
    destruct.'
